  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nI was adding an account from the account explorer. To do so, you need to enter your Status password. However, the screen has no password input on it:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15470435/64873008-247e0380-d640-11e9-81cc-8b372b9dc728.png)\r\n\r\nI am unable to move past this screen to generate a new account.\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\n\r\nOddly enough, on the same build, when I did the same thing from a different root key, I was able to enter my password and add a second account to the explorer. \r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- Password input field appears\r\n- Password input field does not cut off pw when entered (this happened the time I was able to successfully enter a pw - it's like the box was too short)",
